                "timeoriginalestimate": null,
                "description": {
                    "version": 1,
                    "type": "doc",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Fitogram allows updating Tax Group on order. So if order is created with one tax group, then payment is created with the same tax group, however later provider can change Tax Group and invoice will be created with different Tax Group. Fitogram always allowed that."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Should we make the VAT immutable for products that are sold and the invoice is already created?"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Options"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "orderedList",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "listItem",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "paragraph",
                                            "content": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "text",
                                                    "text": "Make VAT immutable for orderline if payment is on Obono",
                                                    "marks": [
                                                        {
                                                            "type": "strike"
                                                        }
                                                    ]
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "listItem",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "paragraph",
                                            "content": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "text",
                                                    "text": "Make VAT immutable for orderline if invoice has been created"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "listItem",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "paragraph",
                                            "content": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "text",
                                                    "text": "Make VAT immutable for orderline after general payment has been done and not been refunded/canceled."
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "listItem",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "paragraph",
                                            "content": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "text",
                                                    "text": "Leave it as it is (Legacy bug)"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Clarify and define HOW we want to handle this topic."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "In my opinion we should implement option 3, because once an invoice has been created you are NOT allowed to change it afterwards in Germany. There should always be a correction invoice generated."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Unclear: What is the possible impact in regard to customer success? Could they get a lot of tickets?"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
