                "description": {
                    "version": 1,
                    "type": "doc",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "According to the provider there is a problem transmitting email adresses from USC to Pro."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "If USC doesn't transmit the customer's email address to us, we set NULL as a placeholder for the email in the customer profile, e.g. jivamukti-yoga-school---peace-yoga-berlin, customer Stefanie Klempin:"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "hardBreak"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "https://app.fitogram.pro/jivamukti-yoga-school---peace-yoga-berlin/customers/1426694",
                                    "marks": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "link",
                                            "attrs": {
                                                "href": "https://app.fitogram.pro/jivamukti-yoga-school---peace-yoga-berlin/customers/1426694"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "The provider now copies all the email addresses of the participants of one class."
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "hardBreak"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "When he pastes the email addresses afterwards, all the mail addresses that haven't been transmitted from USC to us appear as NULL."
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "hardBreak"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "Meaning that the provider has to delete them manually, which he finds pretty annoying."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "I'm not sure if it's temporary that mail addresses aren't transferred."
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "hardBreak"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "In case it is not temporary, it would be good to find a smoother solution for the copy&paste process."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
